&lt;li&gt;Effectively manage quick context switching - easily move between different lead types, confirming, rescheduling, re-engaging after breaks&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience in an outbound closing capacity, operating a full sales cycle from cold prospecting to point of sale&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Strong desire to succeed and hunter mentality&lt;/li&gt;
